    ControlDependenceGraph
    Constructs the Control Dependence Graph (CGD) from a given Control Flow Graph (CFG) Instead of computing control dependence using the Ferrante, Ottenstein, and Warren algorithm this uses the post-dominance frontier to compute the dominance edges.
